[Student "S"]
{NORTH cannot see a game unless SOUTH has help in \Cs so she makes a Help Suit Game Try.

SOUTH has 8 points and the doubleton \C K Q so he bids the game.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "2"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "NS"]
[Deal "E:AJT.AQT3.94.QJ64 Q732.82.A8762.T8 985.J74.KQT3.AK5 K64.K965.J5.9732"]
